<p><strong>Q: What is The White Book: Makaveli PDF?</strong>
A: The White Book: Makaveli PDF is a document that contains the writings and teachings of the late rapper Tupac Shakur, also known as Makaveli. It was compiled by his mother, Afeni Shakur, and released posthumously in 1999.</p>
